WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.140
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.140 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 4]

01:19.190 --> 01:19.940
Xiaobangchui.

01:20.750 --> 01:21.730
Starting today,

01:22.160 --> 01:23.060
your name is

01:23.440 --> 01:25.060
Jiang Lifei.

01:34.110 --> 01:34.730
Jiang

01:35.440 --> 01:36.140
Li

01:37.160 --> 01:37.780
Fei?

01:40.640 --> 01:42.140
At last, I have my own name tag.

01:43.110 --> 01:43.650
Look,

01:44.240 --> 01:45.500
Jiang Lifei.

01:46.360 --> 01:49.010
Jiang Lifei. Jiang Lifei.

01:49.670 --> 01:50.730
Such a beautiful name.

01:53.030 --> 01:55.500
Mr. Zuo Qiu is the top cultivator of our era.

01:55.880 --> 01:57.340
He spoke with you alone

01:57.640 --> 01:58.730
and gave you a name.

01:59.110 --> 02:00.220
Is there some fate binding you two?

02:00.270 --> 02:01.060
None at all.

02:01.600 --> 02:02.450
Truly none?

02:03.000 --> 02:06.140
Your master always hates to trouble himself.

02:08.310 --> 02:10.730
Does Mr. Zuo Qiu know my master?

02:14.360 --> 02:15.780
This chamber pleases me.

02:15.800 --> 02:16.620
Name your price.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.300
Don't stay in the same courtyard with His Highness.

02:28.710 --> 02:30.220
Pack your things and leave!

02:30.590 --> 02:31.130
Move aside.

02:32.670 --> 02:33.250
Make way.

02:35.550 --> 02:37.530
Where are these rabid curs from,

02:37.550 --> 02:38.500
without ceasing their noise?

02:39.900 --> 02:41.690
Anyone picking fights shall be expelled from the academy.

02:41.710 --> 02:42.740
Why waste words on those rabid curs?

02:42.960 --> 02:43.650
Do you wish to be driven out?

02:44.040 --> 02:44.940
Who are you calling a cur?

02:45.150 --> 02:46.060
Whoever replies is the cur.

02:48.430 --> 02:49.250
How dare you!

02:49.870 --> 02:51.340
What are you two idiots waiting for?

02:53.320 --> 02:54.940
You may fight, but no swords.

02:55.110 --> 02:55.690
Stop!

02:58.430 --> 02:58.970
Lanya!

03:00.830 --> 03:01.530
Your Highness!

03:02.360 --> 03:03.020
Tongzhou.

03:06.870 --> 03:07.500
Tongzhou.

03:09.080 --> 03:11.130
Don't believe a word she says.

03:11.240 --> 03:13.250
I just wanted a room near you,

03:13.270 --> 03:15.220
so we can take care of each other.

03:22.800 --> 03:23.740
Alright.

03:24.080 --> 03:25.090
It's my fault again.

03:25.670 --> 03:26.690
Just leave.

03:26.990 --> 03:27.810
Give him the room.

03:28.150 --> 03:29.530
That's right.

03:29.960 --> 03:32.250
We're fellow disciples. Let's get along nicely.

03:33.150 --> 03:33.690
Come on.

03:34.270 --> 03:36.740
Let's check out our room.

03:40.760 --> 03:41.530
Tongzhou,

03:41.960 --> 03:44.020
let's pick another one.

03:47.480 --> 03:48.410
So annoying!

04:10.080 --> 04:11.970
Oh no, she spotted it.

04:47.200 --> 04:49.180
This bed is worth a ton of money.

04:49.680 --> 04:52.370
Master would love this to bits if he saw it.

05:01.150 --> 05:02.570
Smells amazing.

05:16.120 --> 05:18.100
The academy is such a nice place.

05:20.200 --> 05:21.370
No wonder they sent me here.

05:28.350 --> 05:29.420
Old man,

05:31.120 --> 05:32.890
I got accepted into the academy as you wished.

05:34.230 --> 05:35.810
But I couldn't find Senior Brother.

05:38.350 --> 05:40.210
Mr. Zuo Qiu seems to know you,

05:41.910 --> 05:43.130
but he won't say a word.

05:44.960 --> 05:46.010
Everyone around me

05:46.680 --> 05:47.860
seems to have secrets.

06:08.680 --> 06:10.010
I'll dig out your secret first.

06:17.520 --> 06:18.890
She was always wary of me.

06:20.350 --> 06:21.860
Now it'll be far harder to draw near her.

06:29.790 --> 06:31.810
The Soul-destroying Threads trap spirits and demons,

06:32.760 --> 06:35.180
but they'll backfire and ruin your soul and meridians.

06:48.200 --> 06:49.420
She's protected by a seal,

06:51.000 --> 06:52.130
plus a fox spirit watches over her.

06:55.680 --> 06:57.010
Those threads won't work at all.

07:00.440 --> 07:01.770
Shanhua is dying.

07:02.350 --> 07:03.890
To repair his veins and save him,

07:04.270 --> 07:06.540
we need the Nine-Tailed Fox's power.

07:08.000 --> 07:08.860
Lei Xiuyuan.

07:22.760 --> 07:23.330
What's up?

07:26.520 --> 07:27.620
I hurried off this afternoon

07:27.880 --> 07:28.620
and accidentally grabbed something

07:28.640 --> 07:29.690
from your bag.

07:34.000 --> 07:34.890
This is yours, right?

07:45.830 --> 07:47.100
Shanhua's wound can't wait any longer.

07:48.680 --> 07:49.890
I'll risk everything, even my life,

07:50.830 --> 07:51.860
to try this method.

07:55.470 --> 07:56.010
It's mine.

08:09.000 --> 08:10.450
You own dozens of masks.

08:11.150 --> 08:12.570
Which one is the real you?

08:19.440 --> 08:20.570
We don't know each other at all.

08:21.640 --> 08:23.450
Why keep trying to kill me over and over?

08:25.320 --> 08:26.420
If you don't tell the truth,

08:31.590 --> 08:33.250
you'll meet your end tonight.

08:35.080 --> 08:35.740
I stuck around you

08:37.110 --> 08:38.210
for a reason,

08:40.080 --> 08:41.300
but I never planned to hurt you.

08:42.680 --> 08:44.450
My master opened my sea of mind when I was a kid,

08:44.920 --> 08:47.380
letting me see all true and false hearts.

08:48.510 --> 08:50.020
Most of what you said might be real,

08:51.080 --> 08:52.660
but I definitely spotted

08:53.590 --> 08:54.610
that hidden hint of malice.

09:00.040 --> 09:01.380
Who's behind you?

09:01.920 --> 09:02.450
Spit it out!

09:10.510 --> 09:11.180
If I say it out,

09:12.230 --> 09:13.610
my brother will die.

09:15.870 --> 09:16.970
It's same reason again.

09:17.560 --> 09:19.330
Why should I care whether he lives or dies?

09:24.470 --> 09:25.260
I can't tell you,

09:26.800 --> 09:28.210
or explain why.

09:29.200 --> 09:29.900
Otherwise... Otherwise...

09:35.510 --> 09:36.060
Never mind.

09:38.920 --> 09:39.660
Xiaobangchui,

09:41.660 --> 09:43.140
I did try to kill you.

09:44.470 --> 09:45.570
Since I can never make amends,

09:46.870 --> 09:48.260
let me repay you with my life, okay?

09:58.540 --> 09:59.420
What are you doing?

10:19.350 --> 10:20.060
What is this?

10:21.110 --> 10:21.900
Some cheap pity trick?

10:22.710 --> 10:23.420
Are you crazy?

10:30.220 --> 10:31.450
I brought this on myself.

10:33.560 --> 10:34.420
It has nothing to do with you.

10:36.470 --> 10:37.210
Leave me alone.

10:40.870 --> 10:41.570
Lei Xiuyuan,

10:42.940 --> 10:44.140
don't think this pitiful trick

10:44.680 --> 10:45.540
will make me go easy on you.

10:48.340 --> 10:49.210
You don't have to.

10:51.830 --> 10:53.570
I've been on the run from the Longming Sanctuary for seven years,

10:54.870 --> 10:56.330
blood covering every step I take.

10:59.830 --> 11:01.260
I watched Mr. Lu,

11:01.940 --> 11:03.690
his family, and the whole village get massacred,

11:05.060 --> 11:06.420
while I hid underwater

11:06.510 --> 11:07.420
just to barely survive.

11:08.350 --> 11:09.140
All these years,

11:11.220 --> 11:12.660
I've never slept soundly.

11:15.110 --> 11:16.420
I'm scared that if I drift off,

11:17.510 --> 11:18.660
I'll get my head chopped off.

11:21.710 --> 11:23.090
You always say I'm a curse,

11:25.830 --> 11:27.260
but you also bring me misfortune.

11:29.460 --> 11:30.610
I can't save Shanhua

11:31.980 --> 11:33.090
or bring myself to hurt you.

11:35.230 --> 11:36.660
I might as well die by your hand.

11:54.990 --> 11:55.810
You're just rambling

11:56.230 --> 11:57.210
to make me go easy on you.

11:59.220 --> 11:59.940
Tend your wound by yourself.

12:00.990 --> 12:01.970
I'm going to look for Bu.

12:02.470 --> 12:03.140
Hold on.

12:04.870 --> 12:06.140
I knew you had a backup plan.

12:14.980 --> 12:15.850
Take your dagger away.

12:17.350 --> 12:18.420
Students aren't allowed to fight privately.

12:19.870 --> 12:20.850
If our teachers catch you,

12:22.300 --> 12:23.490
you'll get kicked out of the academy.

12:35.230 --> 12:36.490
If I ignore you, you'll die.

12:37.400 --> 12:38.610
I never deserved to stay alive anyway.

12:40.440 --> 12:43.090
I've been a burden to Shanhua.

12:44.230 --> 12:45.300
Running from danger

12:47.830 --> 12:48.810
should end here.

12:53.510 --> 12:54.660
Hey, stay conscious!

12:58.040 --> 12:59.380
You went way too far with this trick.

12:59.920 --> 13:00.940
Are you actually ready to die?

13:16.080 --> 13:16.970
No pulse.

13:19.320 --> 13:20.260
He's dead for real.

13:26.080 --> 13:26.810
You said

13:27.960 --> 13:28.810
this wasn't my business.

13:35.350 --> 13:36.610
But I own this dagger.

13:37.200 --> 13:38.540
They'll check the cut and know right away.

13:39.280 --> 13:40.780
How am I supposed to clear my name?

13:41.280 --> 13:42.420
Our teachers aren't blind.

13:42.710 --> 13:43.660
If they investigate,

13:44.110 --> 13:47.180
I'll get framed for sure.

13:49.960 --> 13:50.570
So annoying.

13:52.960 --> 13:54.260
You've ruined me even when you're dead.

13:54.350 --> 13:55.330
I must have owed you big time in my previous life.

14:23.630 --> 14:25.940
He barely survived amid piles

14:26.280 --> 14:27.330
of bodies and endless slaughter.

14:28.110 --> 14:29.780
Maybe what he told me was genuine.

14:37.870 --> 14:39.330
People say bad guys live longer,

14:39.590 --> 14:40.780
so you shouldn't die easily.

15:08.320 --> 15:09.780
I really brought this on myself,

15:10.080 --> 15:10.850
and it cost me big time.

15:47.470 --> 15:48.570
As expected, she went easy on me.

16:17.960 --> 16:18.810
Sleep tight.

16:19.160 --> 16:20.300
Don't waste my medicine.

16:25.870 --> 16:27.810
Could it be that Zhenyunzi

16:28.280 --> 16:29.780
doesn't give up chasing Riyan

16:31.080 --> 16:32.300
and kidnapped Shanhua

16:32.320 --> 16:33.330
to make Xiuyuan hurt me?

16:37.080 --> 16:38.690
If you die, everything's over,

16:38.990 --> 16:40.570
let alone save your family.

16:44.320 --> 16:44.900
Old man,

16:45.590 --> 16:47.060
I'll definitely be better than him.

16:48.440 --> 16:49.780
I won't give up.

16:51.200 --> 16:52.420
I'll find you.

17:42.230 --> 17:43.770
I actually fell asleep.

17:48.230 --> 17:49.180
Quit staring.

17:49.600 --> 17:51.530
These life-saving pills are from my master.

17:51.790 --> 17:52.580
You're lucky to get to use them.

17:58.440 --> 17:59.530
You saved my life.

18:03.340 --> 18:05.660
I repaid malice with kindness. That's huge good karma.

18:06.310 --> 18:07.380
You must repay me.

18:19.960 --> 18:20.730
Still want to die?

18:26.960 --> 18:27.660
How about paying me back

18:27.680 --> 18:28.730
for the pills before you die?

18:29.100 --> 18:30.180
Stay away if you want to die.

18:30.200 --> 18:31.010
Don't cause me trouble again.

18:42.230 --> 18:43.490
You'll tear your wound open moving like that.

18:44.960 --> 18:45.490
Lie back down.

18:51.200 --> 18:52.420
See? You're bleeding again.

18:55.400 --> 18:56.730
My medicine is mixed in your blood.

18:57.100 --> 18:57.820
It's such a waste.

18:58.680 --> 19:00.340
You're... Whatever.

19:01.510 --> 19:02.660
Pay for the medicine later.

19:03.340 --> 19:04.140
Just heal up first.

19:07.310 --> 19:07.940
Thanks.

19:10.600 --> 19:11.900
I'll pay you back someday.

19:11.920 --> 19:12.420
No need.

19:14.070 --> 19:15.250
We're totally incompatible.

19:15.640 --> 19:16.970
Someone gets hurt or dies when we get close.

19:18.030 --> 19:19.340
Better stay away from me later.

19:19.710 --> 19:20.290
Xiuyuan,

19:20.840 --> 19:22.010
why didn't you close the door when you slept?

19:22.160 --> 19:22.900
What if...

19:22.990 --> 19:23.420
You...

19:25.600 --> 19:26.050
What...

19:26.600 --> 19:28.660
What are you two doing?

19:29.510 --> 19:30.140
We?

19:31.920 --> 19:32.530
We talked

19:32.960 --> 19:34.490
all night by candlelight.

19:34.510 --> 19:35.620
It got too late, so we slept here.

19:37.230 --> 19:38.140
Slept here?

19:39.070 --> 19:39.580
What's wrong?

19:40.990 --> 19:42.210
Nothing.

19:42.990 --> 19:44.050
For cultivators like us,

19:44.160 --> 19:45.290
sharing a bed is totally normal.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.210
These are the uniforms from the supervisor

19:48.440 --> 19:49.100
for Xiuyuan.

19:53.710 --> 19:55.820
Why're you blushing?

19:56.340 --> 19:58.210
Am... Am I blushing?

19:59.360 --> 20:00.140
Probably just cold.

20:07.510 --> 20:08.690
This is so pretty!

20:11.750 --> 20:12.970
I get new clothes too, then.

20:14.470 --> 20:15.050
I'm leaving.

20:29.470 --> 20:30.530
Let's head over there, Tongzhou.

20:30.550 --> 20:31.100
Changyue,

20:31.470 --> 20:32.490
how do I bow properly?

20:32.860 --> 20:33.820
I think it's like this.

20:34.700 --> 20:35.450
Left hand.

20:35.700 --> 20:36.290
Tongzhou,

20:36.550 --> 20:38.620
we can learn the immortal arts here properly.

20:38.790 --> 20:40.010
Don't pick fights anymore.

20:46.940 --> 20:48.180
Look, so gorgeous.

21:23.070 --> 21:23.530
Gelin!

21:24.660 --> 21:25.530
Lifei!

21:27.980 --> 21:28.820
Xiaobangchui?

21:39.700 --> 21:41.290
We're calling her Lifei from now on.

21:41.940 --> 21:42.730
Jiang Lifei.

21:43.510 --> 21:44.580
Even if she wears girls' clothes,

21:44.900 --> 21:47.180
she's still a crafty trickster.

21:52.900 --> 21:53.900
Oops, sorry.

21:54.120 --> 21:55.050
It's an accident.

21:55.120 --> 21:55.690
You...

22:02.270 --> 22:02.970
You wretched...

22:04.470 --> 22:05.340
Quiet down!

22:05.920 --> 22:07.380
Or you'll be cast out of the academy.

22:11.220 --> 22:11.770
Sit down.

22:15.700 --> 22:17.420
Your teacher, Mr. Hu Jiaping, has something

22:17.460 --> 22:18.250
to attend to today,

22:18.710 --> 22:20.100
so he asked me to substitute for him.

22:21.180 --> 22:24.860
The sword is the king of all weapons.

22:25.460 --> 22:26.730
So our first class today

22:26.860 --> 22:28.770
is sword-flying.

22:29.510 --> 22:30.900
Walking into the academy,

22:30.940 --> 22:33.100
you saw the five floating islands around the main hall, huh?

22:36.460 --> 22:37.690
The cafeteria

22:37.710 --> 22:39.290
is on the northernmost one.

22:39.660 --> 22:41.620
Just show your name tag to eat at no cost.

22:41.900 --> 22:43.860
But if you can't learn to fly,

22:43.900 --> 22:45.490
you'll get no dinner.

22:47.120 --> 22:48.050
Can we grab any sword we want?

22:49.660 --> 22:50.530
What do you think about mine?

23:28.860 --> 23:29.420
Ye,

23:29.790 --> 23:30.340
look.

23:31.270 --> 23:32.010
I got one too!

23:38.220 --> 23:39.730
What is this?

24:06.070 --> 24:08.820
He was badly hurt and can still fly a sword.

24:09.360 --> 24:10.340
He's unstoppable.

24:20.220 --> 24:20.860
Tongzhou.

24:22.550 --> 24:23.820
Tongzhou, you did it!

24:28.230 --> 24:29.660
You're so amazing.

24:30.230 --> 24:31.210
That was so fast!

24:32.620 --> 24:33.940
I'm still trying to understand the basics.

24:39.070 --> 24:40.100
Your Highness,

24:40.940 --> 24:43.210
we're fellow disciples.

24:43.860 --> 24:45.100
You can't just let me go

24:45.120 --> 24:46.420
without food, right?

24:53.900 --> 24:54.860
I don't mean to refuse you,

24:55.470 --> 24:56.730
but you can't draw spirit energy.

24:56.960 --> 24:57.900
I've got no way to help.

24:59.440 --> 25:00.210
How about lending me

25:00.230 --> 25:02.250
some magic pills or treasures?

25:05.750 --> 25:06.940
Cutting corners only works

25:06.960 --> 25:08.180
for a moment, not forever.

25:08.750 --> 25:09.660
Taking shortcuts would disappoint

25:10.070 --> 25:12.340
Mr. Zuo Qiu, who thinks highly of you.

25:16.790 --> 25:17.660
Lei Xiuyuan?

25:26.400 --> 25:27.340
Show us how!

25:28.710 --> 25:31.010
How could he do that? He was dying last night.

25:31.640 --> 25:32.580
I'll say it again.

25:32.680 --> 25:33.530
Your spirit moves with your mind,

25:33.550 --> 25:34.250
inhales, and exhales.

25:34.440 --> 25:35.140
Figure it out yourself.

25:41.600 --> 25:43.210
Tongzhou, catch up to him!

25:46.510 --> 25:47.900
Following so close.

25:48.470 --> 25:50.620
His Highness really cares about him.

26:22.680 --> 26:23.250
Fly!

26:33.710 --> 26:35.770
I'm going to starve for real.

26:38.200 --> 26:39.900
I can't summon any spirit energy.

26:42.750 --> 26:43.900
This is driving me crazy.

26:52.840 --> 26:54.180
What a big bun.

27:16.600 --> 27:17.860
Smells so good.

27:22.840 --> 27:23.970
She still doesn't trust me.

27:24.790 --> 27:26.900
Pushing too hard will only make things worse.

27:35.840 --> 27:36.420
Lifei!

28:06.990 --> 28:07.900
Smells amazing.

28:09.160 --> 28:10.530
I'm actually good at cooking.

28:12.030 --> 28:12.530
Wait.

28:13.070 --> 28:14.660
Do you know what fish it is?

28:14.920 --> 28:15.900
How reckless to roast it!

28:18.200 --> 28:19.050
Who cares what fish it is?

28:19.440 --> 28:20.340
My master said

28:20.790 --> 28:22.660
every living thing has a spirit. Don't waste it.

28:22.790 --> 28:23.860
Eat it to top up my spirit energy.

28:31.200 --> 28:32.420
Since you saved me,

28:33.230 --> 28:33.860
taste it first.

28:35.750 --> 28:36.450
Super fresh.

28:38.680 --> 28:40.140
You are using me to test the poison!

28:46.470 --> 28:47.860
You can fly a sword,

28:47.960 --> 28:48.770
yet you dare sneak food.

28:49.470 --> 28:50.140
Your Highness.

28:54.230 --> 28:54.860
This is for me?

28:56.920 --> 28:57.620
Let me check.

29:03.790 --> 29:04.490
What's this?

29:07.710 --> 29:10.010
I hunted this spirit fish after great trouble.

29:10.160 --> 29:11.900
Eating it can boost your cultivation and prolong life.

29:12.920 --> 29:14.490
I made it just for Your Highness.

29:17.990 --> 29:19.420
It died violently,

29:19.440 --> 29:20.340
full of lingering resentment.

29:21.030 --> 29:22.380
A vengeful fish ghost might possess you.

29:24.270 --> 29:24.970
No way.

29:25.680 --> 29:26.490
You never know.

29:29.310 --> 29:29.900
It vanished.

29:48.550 --> 29:49.140
Lifei.

30:10.550 --> 30:12.690
Weak spirit energy. She should be fine.

30:13.750 --> 30:14.860
We'll check her condition tomorrow morning.

30:15.400 --> 30:17.450
I'll take her back and watch over her.

30:18.710 --> 30:19.210
Sit down.

30:24.640 --> 30:26.010
We're fellow disciples

30:26.270 --> 30:27.340
and ate fish together.

30:28.120 --> 30:29.140
I can't just ignore her troubles.

30:30.960 --> 30:32.180
You lower your status

30:32.360 --> 30:33.340
to be nice to Lifei.

30:34.680 --> 30:35.900
Are you using her to win me over?

30:38.230 --> 30:39.660
If I want to recruit you,

30:40.070 --> 30:41.250
I wouldn't need to use anyone else.

30:48.640 --> 30:49.860
You can stay if you're worried about her.

30:50.680 --> 30:51.690
Make do for the night.

31:24.280 --> 31:25.050
Morning.

31:43.480 --> 31:44.500
I promise I won't blab.

31:45.270 --> 31:45.850
Don't worry.

31:57.040 --> 31:57.820
Morning.

32:05.040 --> 32:05.890
I'm going back.

32:11.640 --> 32:12.650
Why rush off?

32:12.670 --> 32:13.700
You two can keep chatting.

32:13.950 --> 32:14.500
Wait.

32:14.720 --> 32:15.420
What to chat about?

32:16.720 --> 32:17.260
Yeah.

32:17.470 --> 32:18.700
What's there to chat about?

32:23.640 --> 32:24.850
Move out of my way!

32:24.950 --> 32:26.540
How come she's in your room?

32:28.640 --> 32:29.010
Well...

32:29.030 --> 32:31.060
What's going on?

32:31.310 --> 32:31.900
You said

32:31.920 --> 32:34.500
you hate others entering your room!

32:36.750 --> 32:38.370
You even shared the bed with her?

32:38.750 --> 32:40.980
I've never shared a bed with you.

32:41.000 --> 32:42.140
Why her?

32:42.160 --> 32:43.090
I didn't.

32:44.080 --> 32:44.450
Oh.

32:44.520 --> 32:46.730
Absolutely nothing happened.

32:47.000 --> 32:48.180
Don't talk nonsense.

32:48.440 --> 32:49.340
I'll beat you to death!

32:49.360 --> 32:52.140
Lanya, you're so fiery early in the morning.

32:52.160 --> 32:53.900
An eye for an eye makes the whole world blind.

32:54.000 --> 32:55.500
Go. We're leaving.

32:56.080 --> 32:56.730
See you.

32:56.870 --> 32:57.650
Let's go!

32:58.750 --> 33:02.340
My Little Wen! My Little Wen!

33:03.120 --> 33:05.340
I took good care of you for three years,

33:05.840 --> 33:09.370
yet you're gone just like that.

33:11.190 --> 33:12.820
Senior, check it again.

33:14.230 --> 33:15.820
My Little Wen!

33:18.150 --> 33:21.170
- I kept you for three years. - Tongzhou,

33:21.390 --> 33:22.740
stay away from these two nuisances.

33:23.910 --> 33:28.020
Can't believe I'm mourning you,

33:28.520 --> 33:29.930
my little fish today.

33:31.950 --> 33:32.780
Bu,

33:33.430 --> 33:34.410
who died?

33:36.800 --> 33:38.260
My Little Wen.

33:40.630 --> 33:42.820
It never hurt anyone,

33:43.430 --> 33:45.260
but ended up dead like this.

33:46.040 --> 33:48.340
The heavens are unfair!

33:49.390 --> 33:52.540
Bu, dead fish can't come back.

33:52.880 --> 33:53.740
Try not to be too sad.

33:54.230 --> 33:54.890
My condolences.

33:55.600 --> 33:56.130
No way.

33:57.230 --> 33:59.410
Little Wen is a spirit fish that lived for 60 years.

33:59.760 --> 34:01.450
I'm tracking down the killer to get revenge.

34:04.360 --> 34:06.970
Little Wen, if you have a spirit,

34:08.040 --> 34:10.260
show me who ate you.

34:11.040 --> 34:11.930
I want to see

34:12.200 --> 34:13.620
who had the nerve to do this.

34:31.160 --> 34:32.620
You killer!

34:33.360 --> 34:34.010
It's...

34:36.160 --> 34:37.660
You killer!

34:42.880 --> 34:45.560
[Hu Jiaping, Chufeng Academy]

34:49.760 --> 34:51.450
I can smell my special spice all over him.

34:53.320 --> 34:54.780
So it was his doing.

34:54.800 --> 34:56.300
He stole the fish.

34:57.380 --> 34:58.340
So infuriating.

34:59.430 --> 35:00.970
Let's watch Bu give him a hard lesson.

35:05.700 --> 35:06.620
Mr. Hu,

35:08.820 --> 35:10.820
Little Wen got eaten by you.

35:10.990 --> 35:12.570
What a lucky fate for it!

35:17.900 --> 35:18.370
Wait!

35:18.780 --> 35:19.370
Bu,

35:20.030 --> 35:22.050
the fish bones pointed at him.

35:22.180 --> 35:23.340
He is the killer!

35:23.910 --> 35:24.450
Shut your mouth!

35:25.070 --> 35:27.180
This is Mr. Hu Jiaping, the head teacher

35:27.220 --> 35:28.530
for all your major lessons.

35:29.240 --> 35:30.340
Mr. Hu

35:30.660 --> 35:33.660
is the direct disciple of Immortal Guangwei from Wuyue Court

35:33.700 --> 35:36.740
and the strongest cultivation master in our academy.

35:37.550 --> 35:38.180
Mr. Hu,

35:38.550 --> 35:40.820
these new disciples just got here

35:40.860 --> 35:41.530
and don't know the rules.

35:41.990 --> 35:42.930
Hope they didn't bother you.

35:43.110 --> 35:43.890
It's fine.

35:44.700 --> 35:46.370
Honestly, I didn't know

35:46.860 --> 35:48.140
who cooked the fish either.

35:52.380 --> 35:53.090
Bu,

35:53.820 --> 35:55.530
since Little Wen had this fate,

35:55.780 --> 35:57.340
bury it so it can rest in peace

35:57.700 --> 35:58.930
in the afterlife.

36:22.380 --> 36:23.300
It's him.

36:26.300 --> 36:27.450
Elder Zhu said

36:27.820 --> 36:29.140
among the new disciples,

36:29.340 --> 36:32.370
you have top-tier spirit roots

36:32.860 --> 36:34.050
and amazing natural talent.

36:34.900 --> 36:37.300
I want to figure out your strengths

36:37.900 --> 36:39.620
to tailor teaching for you.

36:40.180 --> 36:40.970
That's why

36:41.380 --> 36:42.970
I'm testing your strength today.

36:45.380 --> 36:48.050
Mr. Hu, we've just entered the academy

36:48.070 --> 36:49.530
and haven't built up our base yet.

36:49.900 --> 36:51.010
That's exactly

36:51.380 --> 36:53.090
why I need to see how strong

36:53.430 --> 36:54.890
each of you really is.

36:56.240 --> 36:56.820
Alright.

36:58.390 --> 37:01.370
Bring out all your best moves.

38:03.340 --> 38:03.820
Xiuyuan,

38:04.110 --> 38:05.140
how did she do that?

38:05.430 --> 38:05.970
No clue.

38:07.510 --> 38:08.370
Move aside!

38:24.950 --> 38:26.090
Your Highness!

38:49.720 --> 38:50.340
Are you alright?

38:56.070 --> 38:57.300
With mediocre aptitude,

38:58.180 --> 38:59.860
you won't go far.

39:02.720 --> 39:03.890
Keep training hard.

39:13.340 --> 39:14.450
I've got pills to protect the heart and meridians.

39:15.820 --> 39:16.450
Your Highness,

39:17.220 --> 39:17.700
well,

39:18.900 --> 39:19.970
I'm hurt, too.

39:25.860 --> 39:26.660
Here you are,

39:28.550 --> 39:29.140
Thanks.

39:34.660 --> 39:35.180
Lifei,

39:37.300 --> 39:38.180
I have medicine for you.

39:39.260 --> 39:40.570
Gelin, only you're nice to me,

39:41.470 --> 39:42.740
unlike someone else.

39:49.990 --> 39:51.450
This teacher's really weird.

39:51.990 --> 39:52.860
Why test our skills

39:53.240 --> 39:54.620
for no reason?

39:56.470 --> 39:59.300
Maybe he wants to put us in our place

39:59.910 --> 40:01.050
and show who's the boss.

40:02.900 --> 40:03.530
Super strange.

40:04.550 --> 40:05.300
If

40:06.340 --> 40:07.660
he's our main teacher,

40:08.030 --> 40:10.140
we'll never catch a break.

40:10.660 --> 40:11.860
There are loads of teachers here.

40:12.700 --> 40:14.300
Can we beg Mr. Zuo Qiu to replace him?

40:14.700 --> 40:15.700
Don't even think about it.

40:16.110 --> 40:17.780
Word has it

40:17.820 --> 40:19.530
that Mr. Hu has been teaching for over 30 years.

40:19.910 --> 40:20.700
He's extremely powerful,

40:20.720 --> 40:21.860
and Mr. Zuo thinks highly of him.

40:22.110 --> 40:23.050
He won't replace him.

40:23.430 --> 40:24.260
Over 30 years?

40:29.550 --> 40:31.970
He must have met Senior Brother then.

40:37.590 --> 40:38.300
Mr. Hu.

40:41.110 --> 40:42.050
What are you doing here?

40:42.900 --> 40:44.140
You can't even fly a sword,

40:44.700 --> 40:45.620
yet you're running around.

40:48.070 --> 40:49.090
I cooked this.

40:51.300 --> 40:52.890
Roasted bird, fish,

40:52.910 --> 40:54.450
and rabbit.

40:54.470 --> 40:55.370
You name it.

40:55.950 --> 40:57.780
I cooked them just for you.

41:10.900 --> 41:12.260
You cooked well.

41:13.380 --> 41:13.970
Go ahead.

41:14.720 --> 41:15.530
What do you want?

41:20.720 --> 41:22.660
Mr. Hu, you've been at the academy for ages.

41:23.070 --> 41:24.180
Have you ever seen this person?

41:26.180 --> 41:27.700
Who drew this ugly mess?

41:28.700 --> 41:29.370
My master.

41:30.720 --> 41:31.660
I mean, my former master,

41:31.780 --> 41:32.530
Wu Gen.

41:40.380 --> 41:41.220
Who's the guy in the picture?

41:42.390 --> 41:43.180
My senior brother.

41:44.430 --> 41:45.340
I heard he's super strong.

41:48.380 --> 41:52.180
This man with twisted features and triangular eyes

41:52.380 --> 41:53.340
is your senior brother?

41:53.660 --> 41:54.140
Yeah.

41:54.820 --> 41:56.300
Before my master disappeared,

41:56.700 --> 41:57.860
he told me to find him.

42:01.820 --> 42:02.570
I'm telling you,

42:02.780 --> 42:04.340
there is no such person in our academy.

42:04.470 --> 42:05.570
Anyone who looks that hideous

42:05.590 --> 42:07.090
wouldn't even get through the gate,

42:07.110 --> 42:07.700
you know?

42:08.240 --> 42:10.140
Did my master trick me here

42:10.240 --> 42:11.140
on purpose just because

42:11.430 --> 42:13.220
I have no spirit energy and can't help him?

42:15.900 --> 42:16.860
If I can't find my senior brother,

42:17.180 --> 42:18.050
I'll train hard by myself

42:18.070 --> 42:18.890
and find my master.

42:20.300 --> 42:21.700
That old man wants to ditch me?

42:21.720 --> 42:22.300
No way.

42:22.470 --> 42:23.570
Train hard?

42:24.110 --> 42:26.890
You're weak all over with mediocre aptitude.

42:26.910 --> 42:28.140
You can't even fly a sword.

42:28.380 --> 42:29.260
I'd say

42:29.550 --> 42:30.860
don't bother struggling.

42:30.990 --> 42:32.410
Hard work pays off.

42:32.430 --> 42:33.260
I'll keep trying.

42:34.240 --> 42:35.410
No offense,

42:35.950 --> 42:37.660
but you're not even useful enough to be drained.

42:38.380 --> 42:39.620
How are you going to change your fate?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.790
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.790 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves, the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
